title: Turkey's Erdogan calls snap election
text:
Turkey's Erdogan calls snap election 12:28pm EDT - 01:17 
President Tayyip Erdogan has brought Turkey's presidential and parliamentary election forward by more than a year, in order to switch to an executive presidency created by a narrowly-won referendum last year.
